title: on_idle()
brief: Called when the client is idle.
----

<p>If you define the function <tt>on_idle</tt> it will be regularly called when the client is idle.</p>
<p>For example:</p>
<pre>
function on_idle()
   msg( "The client is idle " .. os.date() );
end
</pre>
<p class="seealso">See also <a href="on_exit.html">on_exit()</a>.</p>